column5: Cedar park is just 25 minutes north of downtown Austin & 10-15 minutes from the Domain. Great restaurants & shopping minutes from the house.   Access to the kitchen & your own private bath. Parking included. Great place to escape all the noise & traffic that downtown has but yet still a short drive to several spots.   Recently engaged couple hoping to meet travelers from all over! We are always down for a fun time, but obviously have full time jobs & ask that you respect that   Book now!
